  02 Apr 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  wifiscanner-1.0.1-r1.ebuild, wifiscanner-1.0.1-r2.ebuild:
  Use net-libs/libpcap instead of virtual/libpcap wrt #358835.

  23 Aug 2008; Doug Goldstein <cardoe@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  add GLEP 56 USE flag desc from use.local.desc

*wifiscanner-1.0.1-r2 (23 Dec 2006)

  23 Dec 2006; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org>
  +wifiscanner-1.0.1-r2.ebuild:
  Patch ebuild to use wiretap library from wireshark, fix by Cedric Krier
  <cedk at gentoo dot org>. Fixes bug 146286, reported by Alexander Skwar
  <askwar at digitalprojects dot com>.

  22 Oct 2006; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org>
  wifiscanner-1.0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64 keyword. Bug #133248.

  25 Jul 2006; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org>
  -wifiscanner-1.0.1.ebuild:
  removed wifiscanner-1.0.1 in order to complete transition to ethereal

*wifiscanner-1.0.1-r1 (20 Jul 2006)

  20 Jul 2006; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org>
  -wifiscanner-0.9.6.ebuild, +wifiscanner-1.0.1-r1.ebuild:
  removed old version. bumped 1.0.1 to use wireshark's wiretap library rather
  than ethereal - bug #141154

*wifiscanner-1.0.1 (02 Jan 2006)

  02 Jan 2006; Stefan Schweizer <genstef@gentoo.org>
