  <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> in bug 111364

  20 Aug 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org>
  wifiscanner-0.9.6.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc (bug #102855).

  29 Apr 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org>
  wifiscanner-0.9.6.ebuild:
  net-libs/libpcap -> virtual/libpcap

*wifiscanner-0.9.6 (26 Feb 2005)

  26 Feb 2005; Stefan Schweizer <genstef@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
